Class RptConduitImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.RptConduitImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, RptConduit, Storable
public class RptConduitImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements RptConduit
A RptConduit is a client<->server communication-channel for requesting and returning reports. (Note that a RptConduit is a non-persistent SONAR object.)
Author:
John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting
